information: plasterego® is a modern reality and at the same time ambassador of craftsmanship. always oriented to safeguard the ancient sart of the decorator. since its establishment, it has always been geared to protecting the ancient craft of decorator. the company's heritage is given also by the high specialization of its staff that, like a craft shop, has been forming over time, able to control the development of each project in each realization phase. the high share of handcrafted work within the entire production chain, gives a strong handcrafting connotation to its works, allowing total customization of plaster elements satisfying any artistic and technical need from customers. plasterego® represents craftsmanship, tailored services and artistic manufacture. plaster mouldings plasterego®, are decorative elements that allow to finish any premise in an original and always different way, choosing between various ornamental motifs that most suits customer’s stylistic desires and needs as: shatter frames to be placed between wall and ceiling, trims for borders of walls and ceilings, frames for indirect light providing the spread of light, classic style frames, decorated friezes. plasterego® is responsible for the production of plaster frames in their premises, looking after every single production stage, in order to guarantee a quality product for the customer. the use of modern technologies and the knowledge of skilled workers make plasterego® frames real objects of design.

information: ~more than 75 years of history since 1946 we are dental manufacturer, producing alginates, silicones, cements and plaster for dentists. with kromopan, the first chromatic alginate, lascod has revolutionized the world of dentistry by allowing the taking of high quality impressions with easy control of the processing phases. read our history to find out all the steps that led us to be one of the most important dental industry in the world. highly skilled personnel, more than 75 years of presence on the market, a worldwide distribution network, product quality recognition together with modern manufacturing capacity, packing and logistics have made lascod a point of reference in the dental field. we devote ourselves with passion to the constant development of the products and technologies applied to them
min_headcount: the development of new markets, the training and updating of the people who work in or with lascod with the aim of pursuing excellence in the various business sectors, while always paying the utmost attention to the needs of those who made us reach this important goal: the customer.~

company_name: pr group italia by colorificio rama srl
products_and_services: emulsion paints | manufacture of gypsum mouldings | 3d gypsum modular panels | building materials and products | decorations and illuminations
information: ~pr group italia is a professional in the indoor and outdoor decoration and finishing of a building. we have been producing a wide variety of emulsion paints and gypsum plaster decorations since forty years, preserving an ancient handmade eco-friendly craft, we though renew continuously according to the need of our times. our paints range from water-based products to our decorative effects, fixatives and specialties
min_headcount: while our gypsum plaster design mouldings chracterize themselves for the rich choice of patterns and for having a water-repellent version, to be used outdoors. we complete the offer with a series of 3d modular gypsum panels. unique worldwide, as being backlit. our artistry and experience are at the service of professionals designer and contractors - and final customers alike, from the first idea of the project to its completion, both with our ready-made production and with customised solutions.~

address: via molino 14 | 31050 badoere di morgano - italy
products_and_services: ornamental pottery | high-quality terracotta vases | terracotta pots | hand finished pottery
information: our company specializes in producing artistic terracotta pots of small and medium-sized, suitable for any use, either for live plants for dried flower arrangements or cultivation of succulents, as well as indoor and outdoor furniture.the finishing of the articles provide for the possibility of keeping the clay in its natural colour or hand-decorated, and to provide it with a glaze or slip hot.apart from the vessels, our product range is also composed of saucers, wall pictures, animals and various accessories that you can find in our catalogue.our thirty years experience in the field also allows us to produce, on demand, including exclusive models of pottery of various kinds and use.the clay that we use for all our products, clay galestro colorobbia comes exclusively from tuscany. this type of clay, of the highest quality, delivers a frost resistance of up to very low temperatures and a constant colour over time.all items are hand-finished and are used for molding plaster molds.

products_and_services: crushing and grinding machinery | rotary dryers | air classifying systems | dry mortars for building industry | machines and equipment for mixing
information: cimma ing. morandotti & c. srl is operating in the design and construction of machines and plants for processing powders, in particular grinding and pulverizing, machines, screening machines, air classifiers, dryers, dedusting filters, pneumatic transports and mixers. with the experience and the know-how acquired along the years, cimma designs and supplies machines and complete industrial units in many fields such as production of dry mortars and plaster, processing of lime and limestone, fine grinding of minerals, preparation of raw materials for the ceramic industry, chemical industry, pulverizing of solid fuels, feed and food cimma manufactures a wide range of machines such as grinding mills, pulverizing systems, air classifiers, rotary dryers, paddle mixers, dosing systems and accessories for pneumatic transport.according to customers' requirements and thanks to its large know how, cimma ing. morandotti & c. srl supplies different solutions for complete production lines.
